WEBVTT

00:11.140 --> 00:12.420
[The Chosen Corporate drone]

00:11.320 --> 00:13.110
She, an ordinary corporate drone,

00:13.110 --> 00:16.079
[Xie Yong'er]

00:13.160 --> 00:15.620
transmigrated
into a book as cannon fodder.

00:15.800 --> 00:17.390
He, a wise lord of his era,

00:17.710 --> 00:19.640
endures humiliation
for the sake of the world.

00:17.800 --> 00:19.740
[Xiahou Bo]

00:19.800 --> 00:21.440
If I can win his heart

00:21.640 --> 00:22.510
before Yu Wanyin,

00:22.510 --> 00:23.970
I can survive till the end.

00:24.230 --> 00:25.600
She... is so special,

00:25.830 --> 00:27.360
unlike ordinary consorts.

00:27.710 --> 00:28.840
Was their encounter

00:29.030 --> 00:31.480
a scheme or fate?

00:32.350 --> 00:33.200
Coming soon,

00:33.470 --> 00:36.150
Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort.

00:37.140 --> 00:39.330
[Wang Cuihua]

00:38.470 --> 00:39.470
Are you done reading?

00:39.470 --> 00:42.550
[Coming Soon][Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort]

00:39.560 --> 00:40.560
Share your thoughts,

00:40.560 --> 00:41.560
but be objective.

00:50.560 --> 00:51.090
Hey, you.

00:51.750 --> 00:52.880
Share your opinion.

00:57.520 --> 00:58.780
Out of the 10 projects,

01:00.030 --> 01:01.090
4 involve rebirth,

01:01.600 --> 01:02.670
3 are transmigration,

01:02.670 --> 01:04.129
and two are system-based.

01:04.400 --> 01:06.070
It feels a bit repetitive.

01:06.640 --> 01:07.640
That's only nine.

01:08.200 --> 01:09.200
What about the last one?

01:09.200 --> 01:10.730
This transmigration novel

01:10.760 --> 01:12.230
is clichéd and outdated.

01:12.590 --> 01:14.680
Just reading the synopsis makes me cringe.

01:14.680 --> 01:16.070
[Coming Soon][Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort]

01:18.150 --> 01:20.680
But the boss has already
bought the copyright

01:20.789 --> 01:21.850
and paid this much.

01:23.039 --> 01:24.640
It's fresh and interesting,

01:24.640 --> 01:26.570
like an uncut gem waiting to shine.

01:27.120 --> 01:29.510
You're quite
an opportunistic fence-sitter.

01:29.510 --> 01:30.350
Fine. In that case,

01:29.770 --> 01:32.140
[Coming Soon][Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort]

01:30.710 --> 01:32.770
I'll leave this gem for you to polish.

01:33.000 --> 01:33.430
By the way,

01:33.430 --> 01:34.229
Finish reading it quickly.

01:34.229 --> 01:35.229
We don't have much time.

01:35.229 --> 01:36.590
By tomorrow morning, I want an

01:36.590 --> 01:39.650
unparalleled adaptation plan
and evaluation report.

01:41.039 --> 01:41.900
It must be fresh

01:42.310 --> 01:43.310
and distinctive.

01:43.680 --> 01:44.740
Tomorrow morning?

01:47.740 --> 01:49.700
[Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort]

01:53.920 --> 01:54.430
I'm leaving.

01:54.430 --> 01:55.430
See you tomorrow.

01:56.120 --> 01:57.640
Cuihua, aren't you leaving?

01:57.640 --> 01:59.440
I haven't finished reading yet.

01:59.680 --> 02:01.430
Just skim through the main plot.

02:01.430 --> 02:03.120
All these storylines
are basically the same.

02:03.120 --> 02:04.520
Why take it so seriously?

02:04.760 --> 02:06.920
I'm already skimming through it fast.

02:07.200 --> 02:08.630
Well, don't be too late

02:08.910 --> 02:10.370
and don't miss the subway.

02:10.630 --> 02:11.470
Got it.

02:13.190 --> 02:13.790
Oh, right.

02:14.710 --> 02:15.910
By midnight,

02:16.150 --> 02:17.680
I'll definitely be asleep.

02:17.680 --> 02:18.520
So let me

02:19.150 --> 02:21.520
wish you a happy birthday in advance.

02:21.710 --> 02:22.470
Hurry up and make a wish.

02:22.470 --> 02:23.329
It's quite hot.

02:24.810 --> 02:25.630
Let me think.

02:26.079 --> 02:27.430
What should I wish for?

02:28.750 --> 02:29.550
Make a big one.

02:30.079 --> 02:31.280
What if it comes true?

02:32.960 --> 02:35.360
Then I wish I could
transmigrate into this book right now

02:35.360 --> 02:36.800
and ask Xie Yong'er

02:37.310 --> 02:39.190
what on earth she was thinking

02:39.190 --> 02:41.520
when she created so many illogical plots.

02:42.030 --> 02:44.760
How am I supposed to find
something fresh in this?

02:47.079 --> 02:48.400
Keep going!

02:55.630 --> 02:56.960
This is bad. This is bad!

02:57.079 --> 02:57.680
Oh no!

02:58.240 --> 02:59.400
It's all because of this long, boring,
terrible,

02:59.400 --> 03:00.800
plot-hole-filled novel

03:01.430 --> 03:05.490
that I had to work overtime so late
and still haven't finished reading it.

03:26.870 --> 03:28.750
[Happy Birthday]

03:34.430 --> 03:37.960
Happy birthday to...

04:18.329 --> 04:22.079
[Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort]

05:43.450 --> 05:46.210
[How dare you!?]

05:46.290 --> 05:50.420
[Episode 1]

06:02.070 --> 06:02.950
Where am I?

06:14.750 --> 06:15.810
What's happening?

06:17.160 --> 06:17.890
Did I just...

06:20.360 --> 06:21.820
transmigrate into a book?

06:22.720 --> 06:23.510
That makes no sense.

06:23.510 --> 06:24.710
Absolutely no sense.

06:25.560 --> 06:27.420
One second ago I was on the subway,

06:28.190 --> 06:29.950
and now I'm inside the book?

06:33.950 --> 06:34.480
So now...

06:37.360 --> 06:38.190
who am I?

06:40.430 --> 06:41.690
My Lady, you're awake?

06:43.000 --> 06:43.920
No, that's not right.

06:43.920 --> 06:45.000
From today on,

06:45.159 --> 06:46.600
I should call you Concubine Yu.

06:45.260 --> 06:46.520
[Mei]

06:47.120 --> 06:47.920
Concubine Yu?

06:49.510 --> 06:50.920
Yu Wanyin,
the one who throws her weight around

06:50.920 --> 06:53.180
and harms countless people in the novel?

06:53.510 --> 06:55.120
Yu Wanyin,
who gets executed with a white silk

06:55.120 --> 06:58.190
by the male lead, Prince Duan,
and the female lead, Xie Yong'er?

06:58.190 --> 06:59.360
Yu Wanyin, whose story

06:59.360 --> 07:02.620
from begging for mercy to burial
takes less than 300 words?

07:04.120 --> 07:05.650
You can't play me like this.

07:06.390 --> 07:08.560
My Lady, there's no time to play.

07:09.480 --> 07:11.340
I need to get you dressed quickly.

07:11.510 --> 07:13.040
Eunuch An will be here soon.

07:15.240 --> 07:16.370
Everyone, hurry up!

07:16.440 --> 07:18.430
[Eunuch An]

07:16.480 --> 07:17.810
His Majesty is waiting.

07:25.270 --> 07:27.730
Seems like
you can't make a wish carelessly.

07:30.240 --> 07:31.560
But what do I do now?

07:32.430 --> 07:34.720
Yu Wanyin truly deserves death,

07:35.310 --> 07:37.000
but I can't just die like this!

07:38.120 --> 07:38.720
Um, you...

07:39.630 --> 07:40.190
M—

07:42.120 --> 07:42.870
Mei, right?

07:43.950 --> 07:44.810
Your Highness.

07:46.680 --> 07:48.480
How long have I been a concubine?

07:48.870 --> 07:49.730
Your Highness,

07:50.310 --> 07:52.190
at the Empress Dowager's
birthday banquet yesterday,

07:52.190 --> 07:53.950
she promoted both you and Concubine Xie,

07:53.950 --> 07:55.750
who entered the palace with you.

07:56.040 --> 07:58.360
Yu Wanyin has just become Concubine Yu.

07:59.040 --> 08:02.040
She must have entered the palace
together with Xie Yong'er.

08:02.040 --> 08:02.840
Maybe I should

08:03.190 --> 08:05.920
compete with Xie Yong'er
for the female lead spot

08:05.950 --> 08:08.210
and try to win Prince Duan's heart first.

08:09.360 --> 08:11.270
After all, Xie Yong'er doesn't know

08:11.270 --> 08:13.600
there's a higher-level me in the picture.

08:13.950 --> 08:16.510
I literally pulled off
a nested transmigration

08:16.510 --> 08:18.720
from reality into a novel.

08:17.840 --> 08:18.630
[Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort]

08:19.390 --> 08:20.590
If we were to compete,

08:21.360 --> 08:22.160
she'd just be

08:22.160 --> 08:24.480
a 2D character in my script.

08:26.270 --> 08:27.000
Although...

08:27.430 --> 08:28.160
Although...

08:28.480 --> 08:31.080
Why didn't I
seriously read this stupid novel?

08:31.360 --> 08:32.549
I don't know the female lead's route

08:32.549 --> 08:34.080
in as much detail as she does.

08:34.080 --> 08:35.600
That's a serious disadvantage.

08:35.600 --> 08:36.600
And what if she...

08:36.600 --> 08:38.860
really does have the female lead's aura?

08:39.120 --> 08:39.789
No, no.

08:40.320 --> 08:41.200
Concubine Yu,

08:41.630 --> 08:43.630
tonight you will serve His Majesty.

08:43.720 --> 08:45.450
Please prepare yourself well.

08:45.510 --> 08:47.310
Don't make His Majesty unhappy.

08:47.320 --> 08:48.840
S-serve who?

08:50.150 --> 08:50.880
His Majesty?

08:52.200 --> 08:52.930
His Majesty?

08:53.600 --> 08:54.200
Oh, right!

08:54.960 --> 08:56.820
The enemy of my enemy is my friend.

08:57.080 --> 08:58.120
Instead of competing
with the destined female lead

08:58.120 --> 09:00.050
for that unpredictable male lead,

09:00.320 --> 09:02.320
I can try another path.

09:06.910 --> 09:08.240
I'm fine with anything.

09:08.960 --> 09:11.220
W-what do you mean "fine with anything"?

09:11.960 --> 09:13.960
I must remind you

09:14.390 --> 09:15.850
that angering His Majesty

09:15.910 --> 09:17.310
could cost you your head.

09:17.510 --> 09:19.360
By then, it won't be "fine with anything"

09:19.360 --> 09:20.560
but "not fine at all."

09:20.670 --> 09:22.840
Your Highness,
regarding whether you'll be fine or not,

09:22.840 --> 09:25.200
please think carefully before you act.

09:26.480 --> 09:28.840
In the original story,
I was always devoted to Prince Duan

09:28.840 --> 09:31.030
and repeatedly turned down the tyrant.

09:31.030 --> 09:32.510
From now on, I need to be more careful,

09:32.510 --> 09:33.320
keep up appearances,

09:33.320 --> 09:34.600
and not break character.

09:34.600 --> 09:34.910
Mei.

09:35.840 --> 09:36.840
Help me do my hair.

09:37.120 --> 09:38.720
I'll handle the rest myself.

09:39.480 --> 09:40.480
But My Lady...

09:41.910 --> 09:43.710
Do you even know how to do makeup?

09:43.870 --> 09:45.400
Who are you looking down on?

09:56.630 --> 09:57.690
Come to think of it,

09:58.480 --> 10:00.510
Plan B is already mapped out.

10:01.080 --> 10:01.880
The first step

10:02.120 --> 10:04.650
is to win over
my new client's favor and trust.

10:05.480 --> 10:06.880
If I remember correctly,

10:07.270 --> 10:10.480
the tyrant in the original story
had a thing for the seductive type.

10:10.480 --> 10:12.960
After Xie Yong'er, a cannon-fodder
character, took that route,

10:12.960 --> 10:15.120
she gained
quite a bit of the Emperor's favor.

10:15.120 --> 10:17.480
And with my current looks,

10:18.000 --> 10:19.480
this debut is only going to

10:19.790 --> 10:21.120
hit even harder.

10:23.880 --> 10:27.660
[Yu Wanyin]

10:24.270 --> 10:26.070
Since there's no way to avoid it,

10:26.440 --> 10:28.900
I might as well turn passive
into proactive.

10:40.870 --> 10:43.870
In the book, Yu Wanyin was the one
who got schemed to death.

10:43.870 --> 10:45.120
But now that I'm here,

10:45.510 --> 10:46.970
you'll have to step aside,

10:47.320 --> 10:50.050
because I'm the one
holding the ultimate script.

10:54.670 --> 10:55.330
Hey, you...

10:55.960 --> 10:56.960
Eunuch An, right?

10:58.670 --> 10:59.320
May I ask,

10:59.550 --> 11:00.790
this bedchamber service—

11:00.790 --> 11:02.990
are there any rules or protocols for it?

11:04.750 --> 11:06.950
Your Highness, please stop teasing me.

11:08.790 --> 11:11.050
I'm saying I don't have much experience.

11:13.440 --> 11:15.790
Then I guess I have even less.

11:19.070 --> 11:24.580
[Yongyan Hall]

11:50.030 --> 11:53.830
[Plan A: Seize the female lead position
and win the male lead's heart]

11:50.790 --> 11:53.120
The whole process is already planned out.

11:53.320 --> 11:54.790
With my experience as a corporate drone,

11:53.870 --> 11:57.910
[Plan B: Gain the new client's trust
(the tyrant)]

11:55.600 --> 11:56.240
there's no way

11:56.240 --> 11:58.900
I can't curry favor
with this legendary tyrant.

12:03.510 --> 12:05.270
Greetings, Your Majesty.

12:25.600 --> 12:26.400
Your Majesty,

12:27.840 --> 12:29.040
Concubine Yu is here.

12:43.550 --> 12:44.750
Greetings, Your—

12:44.750 --> 12:45.390
Get out.

12:46.960 --> 12:47.270
How could—

12:47.270 --> 12:48.000
Drag her out.

12:49.320 --> 12:51.030
This scene wasn't in the original story!

12:51.030 --> 12:52.840
I can't fail before I even begin!

12:54.080 --> 12:54.670
Your Majesty!

12:54.670 --> 12:56.200
Your Majesty, at least look at me once!

12:56.200 --> 12:58.000
-If she doesn't stay to serve me,
-I don't want to die!

12:58.000 --> 12:59.200
she's to be executed?

13:02.000 --> 13:03.320
Wait, bro.

13:04.000 --> 13:05.130
You're the Emperor.

13:05.550 --> 13:07.210
Why are you asking the guards?

13:08.000 --> 13:09.320
Your Majesty, spare us!

13:09.320 --> 13:10.080
Forget it.

13:10.670 --> 13:11.400
Let her stay.

13:12.000 --> 13:12.870
All of you, leave.

13:12.870 --> 13:13.480
Yes.

13:19.670 --> 13:20.440
This...

13:20.960 --> 13:22.360
Well...

13:22.910 --> 13:23.440
What's...

13:23.440 --> 13:24.240
going on now?

13:54.390 --> 13:55.910
Does a villain

13:56.510 --> 13:58.570
really need to be this good-looking?

14:04.360 --> 14:05.870
This author

14:06.440 --> 14:08.300
must be obsessed with good looks.

14:08.510 --> 14:09.240
Hey, you.

14:10.120 --> 14:11.180
Con-Concubine Yu.

14:12.150 --> 14:13.880
Make yourself a bed on the floor

14:14.150 --> 14:15.550
and make do for the night.

14:18.270 --> 14:20.870
Make a bed on the floor
and make do for the night?

14:21.510 --> 14:22.120
But...

14:24.120 --> 14:24.780
"Hey, you."

14:24.910 --> 14:25.570
"Hey, you."

14:26.910 --> 14:27.750
He called me

14:28.870 --> 14:29.670
"hey, you"?

14:30.840 --> 14:32.640
Isn't that a modern expression?

14:33.510 --> 14:34.150
Could it be

14:35.270 --> 14:36.120
he's also...

14:44.120 --> 14:44.920
Your Majesty.

14:46.200 --> 14:47.200
What else?

14:50.870 --> 14:51.440
How...

14:52.510 --> 14:53.000
are...

14:54.240 --> 14:54.790
you?

15:18.820 --> 15:22.510
[Xiahou Dan]

15:21.150 --> 15:21.630
Fine,

15:23.870 --> 15:24.630
thank you,

15:26.320 --> 15:27.080
and you?

15:39.110 --> 15:42.710
[Yongyan Hall]

15:41.720 --> 15:42.960
Has Concubine Yu come out yet?

15:42.960 --> 15:43.630
Eunuch.

15:45.200 --> 15:45.840
Not yet.

15:46.120 --> 15:53.910
[Yongyan Hall]

15:51.440 --> 15:54.370
In the past,
concubines got scolded away instantly,

15:54.670 --> 15:56.870
but this one has managed to stay so long.

16:00.240 --> 16:01.570
She's quite something.

16:03.360 --> 16:05.490
I transmigrated here just 2 hours ago.

16:05.750 --> 16:06.480
At that time,

16:07.240 --> 16:08.500
I was lying on a cruise,

16:08.870 --> 16:09.870
soaking up the sun

16:10.200 --> 16:11.600
and drinking champagne.

16:11.630 --> 16:14.030
Suddenly a stupid notification
popped up on my phone,

16:14.030 --> 16:15.490
recommending this novel.

16:15.600 --> 16:16.530
One blink later,

16:17.080 --> 16:17.720
here I am.

16:18.510 --> 16:19.910
Two hours ago,

16:20.510 --> 16:22.320
I was on the subway
heading home from work.

16:22.320 --> 16:23.450
It was already dark.

16:24.670 --> 16:26.400
So how could you be sunbathing?

16:26.440 --> 16:27.240
Were you

16:27.720 --> 16:28.850
across the Pacific?

16:30.840 --> 16:31.840
I was on vacation.

16:33.910 --> 16:37.040
You're not one of those
legendary alpha bosses, are you?

16:38.670 --> 16:40.600
Whether I'm an alpha, I don't know,

16:40.670 --> 16:41.870
but I am a boss.

16:43.630 --> 16:44.240
My life

16:44.600 --> 16:45.930
is pretty comfortable.

16:48.630 --> 16:49.360
Damn it!

16:49.750 --> 16:50.440
How did I end up transmigrating

16:50.440 --> 16:52.480
to a place without even a bath heater,

16:52.480 --> 16:54.340
waiting to die with a brain tumor?

16:54.510 --> 16:55.630
Calm down first.

16:56.000 --> 16:58.480
Your migraines
might not be caused by a tumor.

16:58.480 --> 17:00.750
If it were a tumor pressing on a nerve,

17:01.120 --> 17:03.450
there should be other clinical symptoms.

17:03.870 --> 17:04.329
Really?

17:04.510 --> 17:05.569
I'm just guessing.

17:07.920 --> 17:09.440
Try to think positively.

17:09.790 --> 17:12.349
What if someone poisoned you
with a slow-acting toxin?

17:12.349 --> 17:14.109
You're quite good at comforting people.

17:14.109 --> 17:14.839
My pleasure.

17:15.030 --> 17:17.400
So have you actually
read this novel or not?

17:17.400 --> 17:19.260
What exactly is my situation now?

17:20.200 --> 17:21.240
I did read it,

17:21.829 --> 17:23.270
but I skimmed through it,

17:23.589 --> 17:24.720
not very carefully.

17:26.200 --> 17:27.160
Simply put,

17:27.790 --> 17:29.120
your name is Xiahou Dan.

17:29.720 --> 17:30.980
Your mother hates you.

17:31.350 --> 17:32.830
Your brother Prince Duan hates you.

17:32.830 --> 17:34.030
Your concubines hate you.

17:34.030 --> 17:35.400
Your ministers hate you.

17:35.400 --> 17:37.060
The entire country hates you.

17:38.750 --> 17:40.070
According to the original story,

17:40.070 --> 17:40.870
I hate you too.

17:41.350 --> 17:42.030
Gosh.

17:42.720 --> 17:43.240
What on earth

17:43.240 --> 17:45.100
did I do that was so unforgivable?

17:47.240 --> 17:48.500
Can I have some grapes?

17:51.070 --> 17:51.930
Help yourself.

17:52.200 --> 17:52.660
Thanks.

17:55.110 --> 17:56.920
The Empress Dowager
isn't your birth mother,

17:56.920 --> 17:58.780
so she didn't raise you properly.

17:58.880 --> 18:00.550
And you suffer from migraines.

17:59.230 --> 18:01.440
[Migraine]

18:01.400 --> 18:03.590
You've been stubborn, brutal,
and bloodthirsty since childhood.

18:01.490 --> 18:01.780
[Stubborn]

18:01.780 --> 18:02.620
[Brutal]

18:02.620 --> 18:05.700
[Bloodthirsty]

18:04.830 --> 18:06.430
The loyal ministers in court

18:06.440 --> 18:08.570
were either executed or exiled by you.

18:09.920 --> 18:11.830
You also implemented
a bunch of terrible policies

18:11.830 --> 18:13.200
that caused widespread public outrage.

18:13.200 --> 18:15.000
According to the original plot,

18:15.350 --> 18:16.880
near the end,

18:17.640 --> 18:18.880
you'll be killed by Prince Duan

18:18.880 --> 18:20.140
in the name of justice.

18:21.110 --> 18:22.310
How exactly did I die?

18:22.790 --> 18:23.920
I think...

18:25.720 --> 18:26.980
you got assassinated.

18:28.790 --> 18:30.240
The later plot was too boring,

18:30.240 --> 18:31.770
so I skipped several pages.

18:39.440 --> 18:41.830
You can still smile
knowing you're going to die?

18:41.830 --> 18:43.030
Now I believe

18:43.830 --> 18:45.960
you really are a boss who's seen it all.

18:46.000 --> 18:47.640
Who says I'm going to die?

18:49.070 --> 18:50.270
Aren't I the Emperor?

18:51.240 --> 18:53.310
Can't I just kill everyone
who gets in my way?

18:53.310 --> 18:54.440
That won't work.

18:54.960 --> 18:55.480
Your power has already been

18:55.480 --> 18:57.480
mostly stripped away
by the Empress Dowager.

18:57.480 --> 18:59.480
It won't be easy to kill Prince Duan.

19:00.000 --> 19:00.600
Moreover,

19:00.920 --> 19:02.070
Xiahou Bo and Xie Yong'er

19:02.070 --> 19:04.160
are the chosen ones in the original story.

19:04.160 --> 19:05.200
All the main storylines

19:04.800 --> 19:05.690
[Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort]

19:05.200 --> 19:06.550
are designed to serve them.

19:06.550 --> 19:07.480
If we kill the protagonists,

19:06.740 --> 19:08.720
[Transmigrated:
The Devil's Beloved Consort]

19:07.680 --> 19:09.960
it would be like
cutting this story in half.

19:09.960 --> 19:11.220
Whether we can survive

19:11.440 --> 19:12.770
will become uncertain.

19:19.550 --> 19:20.410
What about you?

19:20.640 --> 19:21.440
You don't seem

19:21.960 --> 19:23.420
to be a good person either.

19:23.680 --> 19:24.740
I'm certainly not.

19:25.000 --> 19:25.800
I'm a villain.

19:27.070 --> 19:28.670
The book barely mentions me.

19:29.160 --> 19:30.350
I was sent by my family

19:30.350 --> 19:31.680
as a pawn.

19:33.960 --> 19:35.290
Anyway, after you died,

19:35.480 --> 19:37.010
I was buried along with you.

19:37.270 --> 19:38.160
That won't do.

19:39.240 --> 19:41.240
Don't you have any other proposals?

19:41.240 --> 19:41.880
Come on.

19:42.070 --> 19:43.880
You really think you are my client?

19:43.880 --> 19:45.280
Asking me for proposals?

19:48.550 --> 19:49.830
What we can do now

19:50.110 --> 19:52.040
is to control variables bit by bit,

19:52.440 --> 19:54.640
see if we can trigger any consequences,

19:54.640 --> 19:55.770
and then make plans.

19:56.440 --> 19:57.440
That makes sense.

19:59.070 --> 20:00.270
But I have a question.

20:01.200 --> 20:02.310
In the original story,

20:02.310 --> 20:03.370
our two characters

20:03.590 --> 20:04.550
weren't transmigrated, right?

20:04.550 --> 20:04.960
That's right.

20:04.960 --> 20:06.620
Since we transmigrated here,

20:06.880 --> 20:08.550
could Xie Yong'er
still be a transmigrator?

20:08.550 --> 20:09.750
If all three of us are,

20:10.030 --> 20:11.230
could Prince Duan...

20:12.030 --> 20:13.030
be one too?

20:17.850 --> 20:23.320
[Flowchart: 1. Announce the Banquet
2. Leader's Speech]

20:22.960 --> 20:24.890
This brush is too difficult to use.

20:26.240 --> 20:27.830
My Lady, Eunuch An is here.

20:29.920 --> 20:32.400
Congratulations, Your Highness.

20:32.430 --> 20:34.290
Wait a minute. I'll be ready soon.

20:34.960 --> 20:35.820
Your Highness,

20:36.240 --> 20:37.830
Eunuch An is here
to read the imperial decree.

20:37.830 --> 20:38.890
Alright, alright.

20:39.110 --> 20:40.170
It doesn't matter.

20:42.510 --> 20:43.570
It doesn't matter?

20:53.720 --> 20:54.720
Go ahead, read it.

21:00.160 --> 21:00.620
Read it.

21:11.440 --> 21:13.240
His Majesty has issued a decree.

21:13.310 --> 21:15.240
Concubine Yu is now officially titled...

21:15.240 --> 21:15.900
Consort Yu?

21:19.350 --> 21:20.720
The Ministry of Rites is informed that

21:20.720 --> 21:21.240
tonight...

21:21.240 --> 21:22.160
A palace banquet will be held.

21:22.160 --> 21:23.200
The procedures...

21:23.200 --> 21:24.400
Will be decided by me.

21:24.920 --> 21:25.780
Anything else?

21:27.400 --> 21:30.160
Your Highness, why do you know everything?

21:32.310 --> 21:33.710
I'll accept this decree.

21:34.270 --> 21:36.640
Here's tonight's
banquet seating chart and essentials.

21:36.640 --> 21:37.880
Please prepare quickly.

21:37.880 --> 21:38.720
Time waits for no one.

21:38.720 --> 21:40.320
Let's all fast forward a bit.

21:42.750 --> 21:43.550
Fast forward?

21:51.200 --> 21:51.790
Shun.

21:53.110 --> 21:54.110
How did we get out?

21:54.400 --> 21:56.070
We just walked out.

21:57.240 --> 21:58.170
Within two days,

21:59.160 --> 22:00.090
she was promoted

22:00.550 --> 22:02.030
from Concubine to Consort?

22:02.030 --> 22:03.160
Truly rare.

22:07.980 --> 22:08.720
[12 brushes, some sheets of paper,
musical instruments, a central carpet]

22:08.840 --> 22:13.090
[Seating Chart]

22:15.920 --> 22:16.380
This...

22:18.160 --> 22:19.590
This is a drawing of a...

22:19.540 --> 22:23.480
[Seating Chart]

22:20.440 --> 22:21.200
turtle?

22:23.000 --> 22:24.240
A whole night!

22:24.680 --> 22:25.880
She stayed directly.

22:26.550 --> 22:29.110
Hasn't His Majesty
been in a bad mood lately?

22:29.480 --> 22:31.160
How does he even have the mood
to hold a banquet?

22:30.470 --> 22:33.740
[Consort Shu]

22:32.400 --> 22:33.930
Haven't you heard, Sister?

22:34.680 --> 22:37.480
Last night His Majesty
spent the night with Concubine Yu

22:37.480 --> 22:39.070
and was overjoyed.

22:39.510 --> 22:40.720
Early this morning, he issued a decree

22:39.690 --> 22:43.270
[Xie Yong'er]

22:40.960 --> 22:42.030
to make her Consort.

22:42.030 --> 22:44.000
She usually seems so quiet.

22:44.400 --> 22:46.130
Who knows what tricks she used.

22:47.110 --> 22:48.520
They call it a palace banquet,

22:48.520 --> 22:49.850
but it's just for showing off,

22:49.850 --> 22:53.100
[Consort Zhuang] [Concubine He]

22:50.270 --> 22:51.930
wanting to see us humiliated.

22:53.920 --> 22:55.980
We're nobody with little influence.

22:56.270 --> 22:57.510
It's fine if we're humiliated.

22:57.080 --> 23:00.540
[Noble Consort Wei]

22:58.550 --> 23:00.550
But Sister Wei is the Noble Consort,

23:00.680 --> 23:04.030
and her father, Grand Tutor Wei,
is close to the Empress Dowager.

23:04.030 --> 23:06.890
Why does she also have to keep her,
a vixen, company?

23:07.830 --> 23:08.830
Keep her company?

23:09.270 --> 23:09.750
Buh!

23:14.750 --> 23:16.410
Sister Wei, please calm down.

23:20.720 --> 23:22.250
Don't let others upset you.

23:22.640 --> 23:23.440
Xie Yong'er,

23:25.030 --> 23:26.560
how can you be so spineless?

23:27.750 --> 23:29.880
We're sisters
who entered the palace together.

23:29.880 --> 23:31.140
I'm not jealous of her.

23:32.310 --> 23:34.310
With your non-competitive nature,

23:34.720 --> 23:36.580
how will you survive in the harem?

23:40.240 --> 23:43.510
His Majesty is here!

23:45.830 --> 23:47.310
Greetings, Your Majesty.

23:49.350 --> 23:50.000
My dear,

23:50.350 --> 23:51.590
this is specially prepared for you.

23:51.590 --> 23:54.320
Rather than wasting time
testing them one by one,

23:54.550 --> 23:57.410
your idea of hosting a palace banquet
works better.

23:59.550 --> 24:02.160
Your method of placing name cards
on the table isn't bad either.

24:02.160 --> 24:02.720
This way,

24:03.110 --> 24:05.440
everyone's identity is clear at a glance.

24:06.220 --> 24:07.590
[Noble Consort Wei]

24:07.630 --> 24:09.240
[Concubine Xie]

24:09.280 --> 24:10.660
[Consort Shu]

24:10.740 --> 24:12.180
[Concubine Chu]

24:12.220 --> 24:13.710
[Consort Zhuang]

24:17.200 --> 24:17.680
Good!

24:18.350 --> 24:19.550
My beloved consorts.

24:20.350 --> 24:21.410
As the saying goes,

24:22.070 --> 24:24.550
"Summer winds blow through endless fields,

24:25.270 --> 24:27.880
and golden waves of wheat
stretch for miles."

24:29.480 --> 24:31.200
During this harvest season,

24:32.030 --> 24:32.550
and with

24:33.400 --> 24:35.530
the pacification of border troubles,

24:35.960 --> 24:36.310
I am

24:36.880 --> 24:38.080
in an excellent mood.

24:39.160 --> 24:40.830
My consorts, don't stand on ceremony.

24:40.830 --> 24:41.960
Just drink freely

24:42.270 --> 24:44.270
and don't leave until you're drunk!

24:45.200 --> 24:46.600
Thank you, Your Majesty.

24:53.480 --> 24:55.070
As expected of a boss.

24:55.480 --> 24:57.750
You have such a way with words.

24:58.270 --> 24:59.160
Of course.

25:03.000 --> 25:06.130
If Xie Yong'er and Prince Duan
are both transmigrators,

25:06.680 --> 25:08.680
then let's invite them

25:09.000 --> 25:10.790
to eat hotpot and play mahjong,

25:12.160 --> 25:15.490
enjoying ourselves harmoniously
and happily in Great Xia.

25:16.610 --> 25:19.400
[Concubine He]

25:16.830 --> 25:18.960
Is this still the Concubine Yu I know?

25:19.480 --> 25:20.310
Such a vixen.

25:24.400 --> 25:25.260
It's your turn.

25:30.510 --> 25:31.350
Your Majesty,

25:32.470 --> 25:34.270
since we have double happiness,

25:34.350 --> 25:35.110
why not

25:35.680 --> 25:37.720
have all the sisters
showcase their talents

25:37.720 --> 25:39.380
to celebrate with the nation?

25:39.590 --> 25:40.120
Granted!

26:07.550 --> 26:08.160
[May the borderlands
remain peaceful forever

26:08.160 --> 26:08.780
and the people live in prosperity
—Consort Wei]

26:08.810 --> 26:10.030
[May Great Xia enjoy peace and prosperity]

26:10.030 --> 26:11.260
[and provide ample food and clothing
for the people—Consort Zhuang]

26:12.270 --> 26:14.400
Consort Zhuang's writing is elegant.

26:16.030 --> 26:18.070
Concubine He's writing is very neat.

26:18.070 --> 26:19.550
As for Xie Yong'er's writing,

26:19.550 --> 26:21.080
it's both elegant and neat.

26:28.240 --> 26:29.370
So what do you think?

26:33.070 --> 26:34.270
Not a transmigrator?

26:36.270 --> 26:38.470
Perhaps she took calligraphy classes.

26:42.030 --> 26:42.960
Let's try again.

26:46.750 --> 26:48.960
Childish style, rough brushwork.

26:50.070 --> 26:52.550
Xie Yong'er must be a transmigrator.

26:55.110 --> 26:57.240
Why don't you look at these ones first?

26:57.760 --> 26:58.630
[Concubine Xie] [Concubine Chu]

26:58.810 --> 27:00.150
[Noble Consort Wei]

27:00.150 --> 27:00.760
[Consort Shu]

27:01.920 --> 27:02.380
This...

27:04.150 --> 27:05.560
[Concubine He]

27:08.070 --> 27:09.310
What on earth is this?

27:13.030 --> 27:14.480
Don't noble ladies

27:14.920 --> 27:16.720
in ancient times learn to paint?

27:20.070 --> 27:21.400
Should we keep testing?

27:22.720 --> 27:24.250
Let's make it challenging.

27:28.510 --> 27:29.440
Your Majesty...

27:30.160 --> 27:31.760
All you do is write and paint!

27:32.430 --> 27:34.290
Don't you have any fresh talents?

27:35.400 --> 27:37.400
Didn't you ask us to write and paint?

27:38.200 --> 27:38.790
You.

27:40.590 --> 27:41.440
Yes, you.

27:41.960 --> 27:43.350
What are you muttering about?

27:43.350 --> 27:44.880
Play a piece of music for me!

27:51.000 --> 27:51.310
I...

27:51.750 --> 27:53.110
I can't.

27:53.640 --> 27:55.310
You'll have to do it anyway.

27:57.440 --> 27:58.240
Well...

27:58.680 --> 28:00.880
play something I haven't heard before.

28:01.160 --> 28:02.680
If I've heard it before,

28:03.680 --> 28:05.480
I'll have you buried on the spot.

28:08.030 --> 28:08.960
Your Majesty...

28:13.920 --> 28:14.920
Here's my chance.

28:19.790 --> 28:20.590
Your Majesty,

28:21.030 --> 28:22.890
I'm willing to play a piece for you

28:23.070 --> 28:24.730
in place of Noble Consort Wei.

28:25.000 --> 28:26.460
She finally came forward.

28:30.070 --> 28:30.670
Thank you.

28:58.880 --> 29:00.680
Holding the pipa horizontally?

29:02.440 --> 29:03.900
Wouldn't that make it a...

29:04.920 --> 29:05.960
Guitar?

29:08.350 --> 29:13.350
What a beautiful jasmine.

29:14.270 --> 29:19.160
Fragrant and lovely on every branch.
-The Song of Jasmine?

29:19.920 --> 29:24.680
So white and sweet-smelling,
admired by all.

29:25.640 --> 29:30.400
-Let me pluck you.
-Definitely a transmigrator.

29:31.070 --> 29:34.830
And give you to someone else.

29:35.440 --> 29:41.720
Jasmine, oh, jasmine.

29:43.350 --> 29:44.000
Bravo!

29:45.350 --> 29:47.200
You're so good at gu—

29:47.200 --> 29:50.240
gusty music.

29:51.400 --> 29:52.330
I never expected

29:53.310 --> 29:54.110
Concubine Xie

29:54.720 --> 29:57.000
to be both talented and beautiful.

29:58.440 --> 29:59.840
Thank you, Your Majesty.

30:00.350 --> 30:01.030
It really is her.

30:01.030 --> 30:02.960
Prince Duan is here!

30:19.690 --> 30:23.720
[Xiahou Bo]

30:28.400 --> 30:30.730
Prince Duan has returned from the border?

30:58.880 --> 30:59.540
Greetings,

30:59.830 --> 31:00.640
Your Majesty.

31:03.960 --> 31:06.090
If this guy is also a transmigrator...

31:06.240 --> 31:06.720
Greetings...

31:06.720 --> 31:07.550
Then his acting skills...

31:07.550 --> 31:08.110
Your Highness.

31:08.110 --> 31:09.550
Have reached their peak.

31:23.510 --> 31:26.160
"These stars
are not the same as last night's.

31:27.070 --> 31:29.930
For whom am I standing
in the midnight wind and dew?"

31:30.590 --> 31:31.440
My Lady,

31:32.070 --> 31:33.530
I don't quite understand.

31:34.240 --> 31:36.510
But you should stay away from this pool.

31:37.110 --> 31:38.840
Last time when you fell into it,

31:38.920 --> 31:41.450
Physician Xiao said
you were practically...

31:43.550 --> 31:44.280
Don't worry.

31:44.920 --> 31:46.180
It won't happen again.

31:47.480 --> 31:48.550
Drown again?

31:48.960 --> 31:50.490
How could that be possible?

31:51.270 --> 31:52.200
Silly Ling,

31:52.590 --> 31:55.050
the Xie Yong'er you speak of
is already dead.

31:55.160 --> 31:55.920
You're all just 2D characters

31:55.920 --> 31:57.590
in the novel

31:57.590 --> 31:59.350
"A thousand trees blossoms at night
in the East."

31:59.350 --> 32:00.920
The story has only just begun,

32:00.920 --> 32:03.250
but I've already finished the whole book.

32:03.400 --> 32:04.130
Xie Yong'er,

32:04.720 --> 32:07.380
your kindness
can't buy you peace in this world.

32:07.680 --> 32:09.200
Let me avenge you.

32:12.590 --> 32:13.960
My Lady, are you upset

32:13.960 --> 32:15.720
because of Consort Yu?

32:16.830 --> 32:17.680
Consort Yu?

32:18.350 --> 32:18.950
Oh, right.

32:19.400 --> 32:22.400
That woman Yu Wanyin
has already been promoted to Consort.

32:22.400 --> 32:24.070
According to the book,

32:24.240 --> 32:26.550
she was supposed to be thrown
into the Cold Palace by the tyrant.

32:26.550 --> 32:27.720
But why?

32:29.550 --> 32:31.010
Could it be that my arrival

32:31.030 --> 32:32.760
caused the plot to go off track?

32:32.880 --> 32:33.210
My...

32:34.790 --> 32:35.680
It's alright.

32:36.400 --> 32:38.330
I'm the woman who holds the script.

32:38.720 --> 32:39.720
In the original story, Yu Wanyin

32:39.720 --> 32:41.520
ran into Prince Duan right here.

32:45.310 --> 32:46.840
Greetings, Your Highness.

32:50.960 --> 32:52.490
Greetings, Your Highness.

32:53.310 --> 32:55.030
Your Highness, it was my honor to hear

32:55.030 --> 32:57.630
your pipa performance
in the grand hall today.

32:57.720 --> 32:58.580
It was truly...

32:58.960 --> 32:59.890
unforgettable.

33:00.310 --> 33:01.510
Just a minor skill.

33:02.350 --> 33:05.280
I've embarrassed myself before you,
Your Highness.

33:06.510 --> 33:08.640
I don't often come to the inner palace.

33:08.640 --> 33:10.300
I wonder if there's a path here

33:10.350 --> 33:12.080
that leads to Changsheng Hall.

33:12.160 --> 33:13.220
It's getting late.

33:13.350 --> 33:14.830
I'm afraid you might take a wrong turn.

33:14.830 --> 33:16.890
May I guide you there, Your Highness?

33:19.550 --> 33:20.010
Please.

33:25.160 --> 33:25.880
Yu Wanyin,

33:26.720 --> 33:28.850
your main storyline belongs to me now.

33:57.110 --> 33:59.040
-Pick out all the bad leaves.
-Yes.

33:59.200 --> 34:00.930
-Clean them thoroughly.
-Yes.

34:06.350 --> 34:07.640
There's fuzz on this.

34:09.110 --> 34:09.960
Be careful.

34:10.190 --> 34:10.630
Yes.

34:11.670 --> 34:12.800
Everyone, hurry up.

34:13.030 --> 34:14.960
His Majesty and Her Highness
are waiting.

34:14.960 --> 34:15.840
Yes.

34:17.989 --> 34:20.060
[Yongyan Hall]

34:24.000 --> 34:25.400
What a feast!

34:45.280 --> 34:46.760
Is your head really hurting that badly?

34:46.760 --> 34:48.360
The original owner's brain
isn't working well.

34:48.360 --> 34:50.560
The pain must have scrambled his brain.

34:50.670 --> 34:52.600
Don't say such depressing things.

34:52.920 --> 34:55.050
There's nothing a hot pot can't solve.

34:58.000 --> 34:59.510
About tonight's palace banquet—

34:59.510 --> 35:00.510
what do you think?

35:01.710 --> 35:03.880
This Xie Yong'er is definitely

35:04.030 --> 35:05.030
a transmigrator.

35:06.070 --> 35:07.470
But as for Prince Duan...

35:08.190 --> 35:09.320
I really can't tell.

35:10.280 --> 35:11.940
Since Prince Duan is here too,

35:12.000 --> 35:12.860
Concubine Xie,

35:13.440 --> 35:14.320
play again

35:14.880 --> 35:15.680
so Prince Duan

35:16.070 --> 35:17.530
can appreciate it as well.

35:19.030 --> 35:23.760
What a beautiful jasmine flower.

35:24.440 --> 35:29.230
Fragrant and lovely on every branch.

35:30.670 --> 35:31.730
Play another piece

35:31.960 --> 35:32.690
to celebrate

35:33.110 --> 35:35.040
Prince Duan's triumphant return.

35:51.320 --> 35:52.000
So,

35:53.150 --> 35:54.800
Prince Duan
probably isn't a transmigrator.

35:54.800 --> 35:55.800
Not necessarily.

35:56.150 --> 35:58.080
What if he just doesn't like music?

35:58.400 --> 35:59.930
My granduncle is like that.

36:00.400 --> 36:01.400
You should have done

36:01.400 --> 36:03.400
a set of radio calisthenics for him.

36:03.960 --> 36:04.560
Perhaps he

36:04.800 --> 36:07.070
would've lost his composure right there.

36:07.070 --> 36:09.150
Wouldn't that expose my identity
to the enemy?

36:09.150 --> 36:10.010
I'm not stupid.

36:11.230 --> 36:13.890
Actually,
whether he's a transmigrator or not,

36:13.960 --> 36:14.960
I have a solution.

36:15.280 --> 36:15.880
What is it?

36:16.320 --> 36:17.180
I'll be a prince

36:17.630 --> 36:18.670
and give him the throne.

36:18.670 --> 36:20.480
It's not that simple.

36:20.920 --> 36:23.110
In the original story,
Xiahou Bo held a deep grudge against you.

36:23.110 --> 36:25.320
The throne means nothing
compared to his hatred.

36:25.320 --> 36:26.850
He's on a path of vengeance.

36:27.190 --> 36:28.280
But we are brothers.

36:28.280 --> 36:29.410
Aren't we siblings?

36:29.630 --> 36:31.160
Half-brothers, actually.

36:31.800 --> 36:32.660
And your mother

36:33.190 --> 36:34.760
had his mother killed.

36:35.630 --> 36:36.960
Then the Empress Dowager—

36:36.960 --> 36:38.000
your stepmother—

36:38.760 --> 36:40.490
made him your study companion,

36:40.510 --> 36:41.960
humiliating and tormenting him

36:41.960 --> 36:43.070
in every way.

36:44.590 --> 36:46.000
That does sound miserable.

36:46.000 --> 36:47.920
And with the same royal bloodline,

36:47.920 --> 36:49.480
in terms of looks, presence,

36:49.480 --> 36:50.510
talent, and cunning,

36:50.510 --> 36:53.360
you just can't compete with Prince Duan,
Xiahou Bo.

36:53.360 --> 36:55.760
You're moody and just living for pleasure.

36:55.920 --> 36:57.780
The world belongs to the capable.

36:57.840 --> 37:00.170
What right do you have
to waste your place?

37:00.630 --> 37:00.920
I...

37:01.280 --> 37:01.880
Wanyin,

37:03.110 --> 37:04.640
I was trying to comfort you.

37:05.630 --> 37:06.110
Why...

37:06.710 --> 37:07.960
Why did you insult me?

37:12.320 --> 37:12.840
Sorry.

37:13.280 --> 37:13.740
CEO Dan.

37:13.960 --> 37:15.760
My professional habit kicked in

37:16.440 --> 37:18.550
and I started giving
character backgrounds.

37:18.550 --> 37:20.070
Well, according to you,

37:21.030 --> 37:22.430
if he's a transmigrator,

37:23.480 --> 37:26.190
then we might have a chance to reconcile.

37:27.590 --> 37:29.150
But if he's not,

37:30.150 --> 37:31.150
then only one of us

37:32.960 --> 37:34.070
will get to live?

37:35.550 --> 37:36.190
Exactly.

37:36.400 --> 37:39.000
You've finally sorted out
the relationships.

37:43.190 --> 37:45.050
That makes my head hurt even more.

37:47.960 --> 37:50.020
Xie Yong'er, the chosen female lead—

37:50.070 --> 37:51.440
I can't see her true abilities.

37:51.440 --> 37:53.240
Xiahou Bo, the chosen male lead—

37:53.440 --> 37:56.700
transmigrator or not,
he's not someone to be trifled with.

37:56.760 --> 37:58.020
As for this Xiahou Dan,

37:58.360 --> 38:00.630
I haven't seen
anything exceptional about him yet.

38:00.630 --> 38:02.560
And he even seems a bit unreliable.

38:03.070 --> 38:04.510
Plus, with this headache problem,

38:04.510 --> 38:05.840
how long can he hold out?

38:06.840 --> 38:07.970
If I team up with him,

38:08.550 --> 38:10.550
can we really take down Prince Duan?

38:10.930 --> 38:13.880
[Xiahou Bo] [Xie Yong'er] [Consorts]
[Xiahou Dan] [Yu Wanyin]

38:17.880 --> 38:18.630
Do you think

38:19.590 --> 38:21.590
I should try to win over Xie Yong'er?

38:22.880 --> 38:24.010
She's the chosen one

38:24.110 --> 38:25.710
and an important ally to Prince Duan.

38:25.710 --> 38:27.400
If she's on our side,

38:28.030 --> 38:29.760
things would go much smoother.

38:29.920 --> 38:30.880
And think about it—

38:30.880 --> 38:32.070
we're all transmigrators.

38:32.070 --> 38:33.670
Who doesn't want to survive?

38:33.960 --> 38:35.920
If we can talk it out,
what's left to fight over?

38:35.920 --> 38:36.850
Don't you agree?

38:38.280 --> 38:40.140
Then go and make contact with her.

38:42.280 --> 38:43.740
So what am I supposed to do?

38:44.320 --> 38:45.400
You...

38:46.550 --> 38:47.880
I need to think about it.

38:50.590 --> 38:52.120
What's that burning smell?

38:52.230 --> 38:54.090
Pleasing His Majesty isn't easy.

38:54.280 --> 38:55.880
Perhaps behind closed doors,

38:55.880 --> 38:57.540
she has some special methods.

38:58.030 --> 38:58.840
Makes sense.

38:59.000 --> 38:59.800
Hurry! Hurry!

38:59.800 --> 39:00.510
The pot is burning!

39:00.510 --> 39:01.310
Water! Water!

39:14.920 --> 39:16.480
-I deserve to die!
-I deserve to die!

39:16.480 --> 39:17.140
From now on,

39:17.550 --> 39:19.550
no one is allowed to enter this door.

39:20.070 --> 39:20.530
Get out!

39:20.960 --> 39:21.480
Yes!

39:28.110 --> 39:28.910
What's wrong?

39:31.030 --> 39:32.560
Your acting's pretty good.

39:34.440 --> 39:35.670
When it comes to business,

39:35.670 --> 39:37.510
you always have to put on a bit of a show.

39:37.510 --> 39:38.710
It's all something
I learned through practice.

39:38.710 --> 39:40.110
I know what you can do now.

39:41.760 --> 39:43.290
Go turn someone to our side.

39:43.360 --> 39:43.710
Who?

39:44.480 --> 39:45.150
Xu Yao.

39:47.070 --> 39:48.000
This Xu Yao...

39:48.320 --> 39:49.980
is Prince Duan's strategist.

39:50.150 --> 39:53.080
He's extremely talented
and exceptionally clever.

39:53.510 --> 39:54.550
It's been 5 years.

39:54.490 --> 39:58.210
[Xu Yao]

39:55.880 --> 39:58.540
When will my father's false charges
be cleared?

40:01.360 --> 40:03.190
Bodhisattva, please bless my father

40:03.190 --> 40:04.720
with health and longevity,

40:05.440 --> 40:07.570
so he may one day return to the capital.

40:08.070 --> 40:08.840
Treasonous!

40:09.550 --> 40:11.080
I've wasted my trust in you!

40:11.320 --> 40:12.440
Then as you wish,

40:12.630 --> 40:14.480
your entire family
will be exiled 3,000 li away.

40:14.480 --> 40:14.870
Without my decree,

40:14.870 --> 40:18.810
[Senior Minister Xu]

40:15.360 --> 40:16.630
you shall not return to court!

40:16.630 --> 40:18.410
The reason he sided with Prince Duan

40:18.410 --> 40:19.070
was that you

40:19.590 --> 40:21.790
exiled his father, Senior Minister Xu.

40:22.800 --> 40:24.280
His father was a loyal
and upright official,

40:24.280 --> 40:26.190
yet you trusted slander,
pinned a false charge on him,

40:26.190 --> 40:28.590
and casually banished him
to a barren land.

40:28.960 --> 40:30.820
Xu Yao was supposed to go with him,

40:31.190 --> 40:33.190
but Prince Duan secretly saved him,

40:33.480 --> 40:36.030
had him change his name and identity,
and hide in his residence

40:36.030 --> 40:36.960
as a strategist.

40:37.840 --> 40:39.240
It's said he never gave up

40:39.550 --> 40:41.110
and has been quietly running around

40:41.110 --> 40:42.230
trying to bring his father back.

40:42.230 --> 40:42.800
Father.

40:49.230 --> 40:50.440
It's about Senior Minister Xu.

40:50.440 --> 40:51.970
Please come inside to talk.

40:53.960 --> 40:55.840
Then I'll just tell Xu Yao directly,

40:55.840 --> 40:57.500
"I can bring your father back,

40:57.550 --> 40:59.670
on the condition
that you swear loyalty to me."

40:59.670 --> 41:00.550
Wouldn't that solve it?

41:00.550 --> 41:01.800
It's not that simple.

41:02.670 --> 41:04.440
He would still harbor hatred

41:05.000 --> 41:06.000
and question you,

41:07.190 --> 41:07.520
"You!

41:08.190 --> 41:10.250
Why did you misjudge right and wrong,

41:10.320 --> 41:13.070
causing my father
to suffer unjust accusations?"

41:13.070 --> 41:13.760
I...

41:15.320 --> 41:17.360
was just a mad king,

41:17.880 --> 41:19.710
blinded and deafened by others.

41:20.710 --> 41:22.030
Loyal or treacherous—

41:23.110 --> 41:25.190
isn't it all decided by a single memorial?

41:25.190 --> 41:28.550
Your Majesty, you knew full well that
Grand Tutor Wei was spouting nonsense,

41:28.550 --> 41:30.480
yet you still believed the slander

41:31.320 --> 41:32.430
and exiled him.

41:35.400 --> 41:36.400
Xu Yao, oh, Xu Yao.

41:36.760 --> 41:38.290
Even today, you still think

41:38.480 --> 41:40.880
it was that wretched old man
who slandered your father!

41:40.880 --> 41:41.880
He's not that old.

41:46.320 --> 41:48.850
Xu Yao, oh, Xu Yao.
Even today, you still think

41:49.030 --> 41:51.110
it was that brat
who slandered your father!

41:51.110 --> 41:52.640
He's not that young either.

41:53.630 --> 41:54.920
Xu Yao, oh, Xu Yao.

41:55.510 --> 41:56.880
Even today,

41:57.190 --> 42:00.650
you still think it was that bastard
who slandered your father!

42:01.670 --> 42:02.070
You...

42:02.880 --> 42:04.340
You're talking nonsense!

42:06.960 --> 42:08.590
If a devil wears human skin,

42:09.710 --> 42:11.370
how can you be sure you can tell

42:12.320 --> 42:13.580
whether it's human...

42:14.480 --> 42:15.440
or a devil?

42:24.590 --> 42:25.990
With such acting skills,

42:27.230 --> 42:28.280
it'd be a waste

42:28.960 --> 42:30.560
if you don't become an actor.

42:43.590 --> 42:44.280
You...

42:45.510 --> 42:47.150
look different somehow.

42:49.190 --> 42:51.390
This is called corporate drone makeup.

42:51.440 --> 42:53.920
Gentle, kind, and hardworking.

42:55.190 --> 42:57.230
I'm going to extend an olive branch
to Xie Yong'er later.

42:57.230 --> 42:58.320
Looking approachable

42:58.320 --> 43:00.450
makes it easier to close the distance.

43:01.630 --> 43:02.360
Women.

43:05.510 --> 43:06.840
You also look

43:07.360 --> 43:08.490
somehow different.

43:10.150 --> 43:12.410
Since I'm going to
turn Xu Yao to our side,

43:12.840 --> 43:13.900
shouldn't I create

43:14.230 --> 43:15.630
a bit of contrast as well?

43:18.360 --> 43:19.000
Men.

43:37.440 --> 43:37.840
This way.
